fix: two issues - (1) rust-embed wasn't picking up frontend changes because build.rs rebuilt the files on disk but never forced cargo to recompile the server crate. Added hash_dir() that computes a hash of frontend/build/ and emits cargo:rustc-env=FRONTEND_HASH so cargo recompiles when assets change. Also fixed Tauri build.rs to always copy newer sidecar binaries instead of only when missing. (2) Task dispatcher silently failed when tasks had no conversation_id - notify_conversation returned early, agent had no conversation context. Now auto-creates a conversation with the agent as participant when dispatching a task without one. Also fixed pre-existing clippy needless_return warnings in docker/manager.rs.
